{"tid":689495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班FBI探員夜店消遣熱舞　打後空翻跌手槍落地走火射傷人","createTime":"2018-06-04T06:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T12:47:41.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4eae246ecac6e0e8033ba65faa99c971214e2f44","tid":689495,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">休班FBI探員夜店消遣熱舞　打後空翻跌手槍落地走火射傷人 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180604/s00005/da442e24f9dcfd45a392126695e53253.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180604%2Fs00005%2Fda442e24f9dcfd45a392126695e53253.jpg&h=253ab2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦調查局（FBI）一名休班探員在科羅拉多州一間夜店消遣跳舞期間，佩槍意外跌在地上並走火，一名男子中彈受輕傷，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地周五凌晨近一時，該探員下班後到丹佛市的Mile High夜店消遣。網上流傳片段所見，當時探員身旁有過百人，他跳舞跳得起勁，蹲下來雙手一揮表演後空翻，其間手槍從褲後口袋掉出來，槍支落地後他衝上前撿起，豈料不慎誤扣板機，射傷一名男顧客的小腿，片段還看到槍口噴出火光的瞬間。他撿回手槍收起後，揮揮手離開。<br />\n<br />\n受傷男子隨即被送往醫院救治。丹佛市警方指傷者情況穩定，警方及後尋獲該休班探員，再轉交聯邦調查局跟進。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查局丹佛分局發言人桑德斯（Amy Sanders）表示，事件屬聯邦調查局人事問題，丹佛市警方主導今次調查，但無交代該探員會否受處分。<br />\n<br />\n(美國廣播公司)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180604/s00005/1528082202541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180604%2Fs00005%2F1528082202541&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkL5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=5f6f7c99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180604%2Fs00005%2F1528082202541&h=0d607dd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180604/s00005/1528082202541</a>"},{"pid":"08cd1ac6d5c7383c4d1624f342ed7b064477b284","tid":689495,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa